  "text": "Its construction can be systematically accomplished making use of intertwining relations for the R ± operators as was done, for instance, in Ref. [CITATION_1] for the hard-hard open spin chains. However, we will not follow this route in the current presentation and rely instead on a diagrammatic technique introduced in Ref. [24] .",
